title: Update failed
body:
I tried starting league the other day and I got an error each time I tried (I'm sorry I don't remember what it was)without it starting up. I ran it as administrator and it opened up, but now when it is updating, it gets to 33% and gives me an "update failed unspecified error occurred" error.I've restarted, I've clean reinstalled, and a few other things. If anyone knows what I can do to fix this I would love you eternally.

replies.body: At this phase in the patcher, the patcher needs to establish a connection to the patching server to update your files.  It looks like your network is being blocked so it can't download those updates.  Go over our [connection issues](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) guide to troubleshoot this towards a fix.  That should help, but let me know if you have any questions!
